latestPosts.caption:
No grandeur. No theatrics. Just two hearts, steady in love, shaping a day that felt deeply, quietly like their own. 🪷🪞
Every details- from the rich maroon of her lehenga to the morning light that framed their vows- was a reflection of who they are ✨

Meragi didn't just plan this wedding. We listened, felt, and created alongside them. 
And then, we paused to frame it all - just like this. 💫

Bride : Mira 
Groom : Mohit
Shot by @meragi.photography
